      "13": "For|strong=\"G1063\"I|strong=\"G2532\"bear|strong=\"G3140\"him|strong=\"G0846\"testimony|strong=\"G3140\"that|strong=\"G3754\"he|strong=\"G2532\"hath much|strong=\"G4183\"labour for|strong=\"G1063\"you|strong=\"G5210\", and|strong=\"G2532\"for|strong=\"G1063\"them|strong=\"G0846\"that|strong=\"G3754\"are|strong=\"G3588\"at|strong=\"G1722\"Laodicea|strong=\"G2993\", and|strong=\"G2532\"them|strong=\"G0846\"at|strong=\"G1722\"Hierapolis|strong=\"G2404\".",
